<section id="about" class="section">
  <h2>About Riff Riot</h2>
  <p class="lead">Riff Riot formed in the underground clubs, bringing raw riffs and explosive choruses to packed rooms. We write songs that hit hard and stay in your head — a mix of classic rock muscle and modern production polish.</p>

  <div class="split">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518972559570-7cc1309f3229?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Band performing live">
    <div class="bio">
      <h3 style="color:var(--accent1);margin-top:0">The Sound</h3>
      <p>We blend crunchy guitars, synth textures, and vocal hooks. Each song is crafted to be big on stage and intimate on headphones.</p>
      <p class="bio">Our catalog ranges from blazing rock bangers to moody indie epics. We believe in loud honesty — and we bring that energy to every show.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:12px">
        <a class="tag" href="#albums">Latest Album: Neon Nights</a>
